Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:38.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must fight the towering foe!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:38.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kyodai na teki o
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:41.47,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fight! Fight! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:41.47,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uteyo! Uteyo! Uteyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:48.27,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Bring to bear the rage of justice, Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:48.27,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Seigi no ikari o butsukero GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:54.61,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:54.61,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:58.53,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Rise once more! Rise once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:58.53,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru! Yomigaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Rise once more! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must seize the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kimi yo tsukame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fly toward the galaxy, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Ginga e mukatte tobeyo GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundam successfully fought off\NChallia Bull's Braw Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.96,0:01:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,However, its control system was no longer\Nable to keep up with Amuro's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro's reflexes and combat abilities\Nhad continued to improve...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.18,0:01:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...making it evident that the Gundam's\Nperformance was no longer good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.97,0:01:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Modifications to the Gundam's\Ndrive system began at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.58,0:01:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...but nobody could say whether\Nthat would solve the problem at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah's Dilemma
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.45,0:02:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it good that Amuro's getting stronger?\NThen the Gundam will be stronger, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.13,0:02:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so dumb! The Gundam can't fight\Nunless it can keep up with Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.98,0:02:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's why everyone's so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.04,0:02:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Go help out with dinner or something, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- Did you talk to them?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They want us to go\Nto Solomon's technical headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.15,0:02:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do the Federation Forces have a solution?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine the Federation Forces\Nare that considerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Mirai. I haven't noticed myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But have Amuro's combat skills\Nimproved that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell by watching his recent battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No. No, that's not what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,His intuition is so good...\Nisn't it like he's seeing the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.04,0:02:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw Bow, you sense it sometimes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro is different now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.91,0:02:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Having said that, I don't believe\Nwhat Ms. Matilda said in the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.89,0:03:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,...about Amuro being some kind of esper.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Human beings can't change themselves\Nso conveniently.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- Of course not. Right, Fraw Bow?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mirai! We're entering Solomon.\N- Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I want all White Base mechanics\Nto step away from the Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.57,0:03:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take over from this point on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry with the magnet coating!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.01,0:03:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.46,0:03:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Amuro Ray, the Gundam pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.33,0:03:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here because I read your report.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't blame me if this doesn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.47,0:03:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, we've never had\Na chance to test it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.07,0:03:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm applying my theory\Nto make the Gundam move faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.55,0:03:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure that's possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:04:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't guarantee anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He's Dr. Mosk Han.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A top electromagnetic engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called a magnet coating.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They're making the Gundam's drive system\Nfaster by wrapping it in electromagnetic fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,See? It's sort of like oiling the joints.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Can they really do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to ask the doctor himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.93,0:04:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand the concept, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to a strategy meeting.\NWe should take off shortly. Got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- Y-Yes, sir!\N- It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.44,0:04:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ditto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a move on!\NThe operation has already begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Challia Bull has been defeated?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was likely due to his inexperience.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Char's reports said the Gundam\Nmay not be tuned to a Newtype's abilities...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That Char. He's always guessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- Pardon?\N- Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.11,0:04:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And what of Supreme Commander\NGihren's strategies?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:05:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Our Granada fleet and A Baoa Qu\Nwill form the front line...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.54,0:05:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...with the Solar Ray at the homeland...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The Solar Ray...?\NYes, that must be Gihren's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The Granada base on the far side of the\Nmoon, and this space fortress, A Baoa Qu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The line linking them\Nis Zeon's final line of defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.26,0:05:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Mahal, the Principality of Zeon's\Nthird closed-cylinder colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Vessel 123, all set!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.37,0:05:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks! Go ahead and take off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You! And you call yourself a Zeon citizen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.36,0:05:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been separated from my granddaughter.\NI was looking for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I guarantee you,\Nyour granddaughter is on one of the ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:06:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't know where her ship's headed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's within Zeon. You'll find her in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- Next group, hurry!\N- Get up! It's your group's turn to go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The mandatory evacuation of Mahal's\N1.5 million residents...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...began four days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It was obvious that this was part of a plan\Nto defend the homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.01,0:06:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Panels of solar cells used at other colonies\Nwere being brought here to Mahal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The residents could only watch anxiously\Nas the preparations continued.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But Gihren...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to evacuate a million civilians\Nonly demonstrates...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.98,0:06:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...your incompetence as a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.32,0:06:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you say that to my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Gihren!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:07:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the man who laid out\Nthis nation's monarchical system.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.29,0:07:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- And I can't support your militaristic...\N- Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear your plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,For our Zeon homeland...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...the moon and A Baoa Qu\Nmark the final line of defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.13,0:07:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,As such, the Earth Federation Forces\Ncan invade us from these three routes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Once they breach the line,\NZeon is exposed and helpless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So we must attack the oncoming fleet\Nwith the Solar Ray before they get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,By using a colony for this system, we'll save\NZeon while also saving time and money.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do, Gihren,\Nafter winning at such cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be honored if you'd sign your consent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already started. Why ask me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Without Sovereign Degwin,\Nthere is no Principality of Zeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And? What are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We've reduced the human population.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.17,0:07:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll maintain it at this level,\Nleaving only the superior races.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only way humanity can hope\Nto achieve everlasting peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.78,0:08:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And it can only be done\Nby controlling humanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...through the dictatorship of the Zabi family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Gihren. Are you familiar...\Nwith Adolf Hitler?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitler...? The historical figure\Nfrom the middle era?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He was a dictator.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.67,0:08:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A man who failed to figure out\Nthe rest of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be following\Nin Hitler's footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.18,0:08:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I established the Principality\Nas a means to quickly unite the Zeon people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It was to make Zeon's ideals a reality.\NBut now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This follower of Hitler\Nhas created a dictatorship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.29,0:08:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Together with Kycilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolute democracy will only produce\Nweakness, as with the Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Humanity will end up consuming itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.16,0:08:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as it's done in this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But I will be victorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,See for yourself how Hitler's follower\Nfights this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I will take command at A Baoa Qu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget that Hitler was defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got it! One ship is a Magellan-class!\NThree Salamis-class!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's their minimum combat unit!\N- Send out mobile suits!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.90,0:09:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Char, shall we send the Elmeth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.67,0:09:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.\NDon't give Lalah special treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Lalah, you're not afraid, are you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This'll be your first actual battle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cover the 2 Rick Doms from behind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll head out shortly myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.54,0:09:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.11,0:09:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Any reinforcements from Granada?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gwarib will be here in 5 or 6 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. It looks like Lady Kycilia\Nhas finally decided to take action...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,J-missile!\NTarget the enemy Magellan-class!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Minus 0.2! Adjusting 2! Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! R 0.3! 2! Left 0. 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.70,0:10:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Aim second J-missile at the target!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.\NI'll head out in the Gelgoog.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mulligan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving you in charge.\NI believe you owe me a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.39,0:10:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- Be sure to do a good job.\N- Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.51,0:10:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you to give me 30 seconds\Nof covering fire after I've launched.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! 30 seconds of covering fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.52,0:10:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hit our own mobile suits!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job, Mulligan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.73,0:11:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, move it, Gelgoog!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack the portside Salamis!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it, Captain! I got them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.48,0:11:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were the Elmeth's bits?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.59,0:11:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She fights like a veteran pilot already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.15,0:11:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How can she do that,\Nwhen she's never fought before?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I'll get at least one more...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The Doms aren't giving me backup?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.76,0:11:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The Doms are retreating...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are they moving behind me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They're sending a first-time fighter\Nlike me to the front?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.51,0:11:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I have to fight on my own?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.18,0:11:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Without support, I can't concentrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Only one more, but...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.36,0:12:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hear it again! It says la, la.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Source unknown!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.42,0:12:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.95,0:12:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Buttsham!\NYou're supposed to be in the front!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.19,0:12:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's crazy! With the Elmeth on our side,\Nthere's no reason for us to fight up front.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.07,0:12:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah! Don't push yourself too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So I shouldn't rely\Non my own shooting skills?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.16,0:13:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah. I'll cover you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.09,0:13:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you're here...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.43,0:13:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! There it is again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Well done, Lalah!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for covering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:14:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...at Solomon, now the forward base\Nof the Earth Federation Forces...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.88,0:14:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...orders are being given\Nfor the next operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This marks the beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...of "Operation Star One,"\Nthe plan to invade the Zeon homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.19,0:14:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Each fleet will take its designated course...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...towards the target "star".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.16,0:14:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Though part of the 13th Autonomous Fleet,\Nwhich is meant to be at the forefront...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.77,0:14:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...the departure of the White Base is delayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.14,0:14:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I have confidence in my theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.41,0:14:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe I've successfully\Neliminated all mechanical friction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.54,0:14:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So in other words, there's no limit\Nto how quickly it can move?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, in theory. However, the Gundam's\Nactual power is another matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.90,0:14:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.60,0:14:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a lifesaver, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.36,0:14:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you survive, then you can thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:15:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want you to find some way\Nto send me the data...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.14,0:15:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...from your next battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it's best not to know\Nwhat people are really thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.54,0:15:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You're absolutely right, Amuro Ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put my faith in\Nyour instincts with the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.35,0:15:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.82,0:15:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- Promise me you'll survive.\N- Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.61,0:15:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can bring back your data, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.01,0:15:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Precisely!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.93,0:15:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to full speed once we leave port.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.37,0:15:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- Follow the forces ahead of us.\N- Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The Elmeth could be more powerful\Nthan your Gelgoog, Captain Char.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.75,0:15:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised to hear that from\Nseasoned warriors like yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We witnessed the abilities of a Newtype\Nfor the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:16:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,With that kind of power,\NEnsign Lalah could single-handedly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...wipe out an entire combat team\Nin a matter of minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,When we became aware of this...\Nit seemed ludicrous to risk our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,With a pilot as great as Ensign Lalah,\Nthere's no need for us common humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you perhaps envious of Lalah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.69,0:16:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the question, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I can't completely rule it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.09,0:16:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But above all, we're truly amazed\Nby the power of a Newtype.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm prepared to face court-martial.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But all I ask is that you allow us\Nto fight behind the Elmeth when it heads out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.96,0:16:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you handle it, Ensign?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I can understand the Lieutenant's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's settled.\NLieutenant, are you satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.67,0:16:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll reach the 13th Autonomous Fleet\Nin approximately 15 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.14,0:16:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Attention, all hands!\NEat now while you still have time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.14,0:16:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be having combat rations\Nfrom now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh! So this junk isn't combat rations?\NCould've fooled me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing. But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, got a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.39,0:17:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.51,0:17:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great, but the faster movements\Nput an enormous strain on the parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.23,0:17:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very hard to find a good balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay.\NHave confidence, Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- You really think so?\N- Of course. You're a Newtype, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,People usually tell me\NI'm an old-fashioned type.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.72,0:17:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds right. You're sentimental\Nand not at all far-out, Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.72,0:17:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,When you phrase it like that\NI don't feel particularly flattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Char Aznable\Nand Ensign Lalah Sune, reporting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The main forces of the carrier Dolos...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.29,0:17:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...have already been deployed\Non the Granada-A Baoa Qu line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.98,0:18:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, you will join my raiding force\Nand take command.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like that outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.36,0:18:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.43,0:18:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Give the supply corps\Nthe Ensign's uniform size.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The supply corps keep insisting\Nwe don't win wars with our clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Make them rush it in my name.\NHer clothes are an eyesore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how was her performance test?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.50,0:18:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroyed two Salamis ships\Nin her very first combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.42,0:18:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah and the Elmeth\Nare a powerful combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.20,0:18:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Two ships? That's very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The time seems right for the formation\Nof a special Newtype combat force.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to see the Elmeth in action.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:18:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That Dr. Mosk is really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.24,0:19:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh no. It's more Amuro.\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.40,0:19:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The way he pilots the Gundam...\Nperhaps Newtypes do exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,"Newtypes"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.51,0:19:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"Newtypes"...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.15,0:19:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright! Amuro's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.75,0:19:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? A fleet battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.86,0:19:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our rendezvous point!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The main fleet\Nmust've encountered the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.87,0:19:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- Who's the enemy?\N- Unable to confirm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.16,0:19:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare for fleet battle!\NGundam and all other units, take off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy force is huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.28,0:19:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost another ally...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's calling me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's calling me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.69,0:19:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.66,0:19:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,One is Char...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:19:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And the other... Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.70,0:20:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Char!\NChar! I have you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.25,0:20:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right to throw everything away now
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.92,0:20:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All alone, I'm left as a corpse\NWhat?! It's getting in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.88,0:20:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,In this battlezone
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I writhe in agony within the flames of hell
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.84,0:20:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I writhe in agony within the flames of hell\NCaptain! Pull back, it's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.92,0:20:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.73,0:20:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.62,0:20:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.81,0:20:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The beam shines\NThe Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.90,0:20:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In the flashback, I see his shadow\NIt seems completely different\Nfrom yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In the flashback, I see his shadow
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Char! Char! Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Char! Char! Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.53,0:20:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't die alone! I call him again and again
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't die alone! I call him again and again\NCaptain, move aside!\NYou're in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't die alone! I call him again and again
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.87,0:20:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking aim, Char is the target
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.87,0:20:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Char! Char! Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Char! Char! Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Char! Char! Char!\NThe Gundam...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.46,0:21:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You hurt the Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.93,0:21:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Char!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.87,0:21:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.24,0:21:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain! Please eject now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's all right.t explode from this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.86,0:21:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But still...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.23,0:21:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to cling onto the Elmeth!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm continuing. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.22,0:21:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But what? What Is It?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My head feels heavy.\NLike something is pressing down on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.63,0:21:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.37,0:21:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're a bad person.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.07,0:21:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.44,0:21:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're a bad person, bullying Char like this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.78,0:21:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you calling bad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.50,0:22:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base made its rendezvous with\Nthe 13th Autonomous Fleet flying ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.01,0:22:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,However, by this time, the fleet had\Nalready lost three Salamis-class ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.05,0:22:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Two of these were destroyed by the Elmeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.42,0:22:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,In total, Lalah had destroyed\Nfour vessels in one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.16,0:22:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This was an unprecedented accomplishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.36,0:22:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But If Lalah's headaches havem pilot...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.54,0:22:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...that could definitely complicate matters.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.14,0:23:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, the battlefield shifts\Ntoward the far side of the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.33,0:23:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The fierce battle between\Nthe Gundam and the Elmeth...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.64,0:23:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...shows Amuro and Lalah a vision of\Nthe destiny toward which they must move.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.54,0:23:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But the battlefield engulfs them,\Nthen spreads to enormous proportions.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.17,0:23:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Lalah will perish.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.74,0:23:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam. Next episode...\NA Cosmic Glow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.88,0:23:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A Cosmic Glow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.10,0:23:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.19,0:23:54.03,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.03,0:23:59.03,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.03,0:24:09.25,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.25,0:24:14.18,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:18.81,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.81,0:24:24.19,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.19,0:24:28.77,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.77,0:24:39.08,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.19,0:23:54.03,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Furimukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.03,0:23:59.03,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uchuu no kanata ni kagayaku hoshi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.03,0:24:09.25,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Omae no umareta furusato da
